    "body": "**Answer:**\r\nAfter update, everything above base fee is given to block producer as priority fee, if using legacy tx\r\nSo say you set gas to 150 and hit send on a legacy tx. Let’s assume Base on inclusion is 75, that’s burned, and the other 75 go to the block producer as priority fee \r\n1559 you might set Max base to 150 and priority fee to say 3, so if base is at 75 on inclusion, then you pay 75 base which is burned, and 3 go to the block producer as priority fee",
